           move      zero                 to   w-tes-tip-mag          .
           move      zero                 to   w-tes-num-mag          .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-num-mag-alf      .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-num-mag-des      .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-num-mag-udm      .
