           move      spaces               to   w-tes-flg-zer (1)      .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-cst-mes-ctr      .
       nor-nok-tes-200.
           add       1                    to   w-det-cst-mes-ctr      .
           if        w-det-cst-mes-ctr    >    12
                     go to nor-nok-tes-999.
